{"tid":419642,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩轉會用iphone,有個問題想問","createTime":"2017-09-30T16:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T03:39:50.000Z","uid":59395,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7a99f7a6e93f4b8cf2804e0fac4b59194e080c","tid":419642,"uid":59395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"小弟本身用AN機,咁平時WTSAPP,FB,自己影D相都係分開唔同FOLDER放既,但IOS FB下載相,WTSAPP D相同埋自己影D相全部都放係相機菲林果個LOCATION<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下有冇得手動改左FB DL相個LOCATION?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我本身係AN機草埋既相搬晒落IPHONE到,個FOLDER叫facebook,但而家FB 下載相又去左佢個相機菲林同其他APP D相撈埋一齊,想睇下有冇計轉番落我自己本身草相個FOLDER到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf0528c0a83ed6c0447165f3a8ea44f9fd42027","tid":419642,"uid":104256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"682029d5e5f6fc67ffb178353cd00fee2a188dc5","tid":419642,"uid":75694,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用過an機 就會知IOS 啲file 係幾咁白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜用咗iphone就好難過返檔"},{"pid":"b4ee4d27ad0ca4e1772b87f5ca8eadf4a26fb95f","tid":419642,"uid":59395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5528ee928c8470eb8070e1769ab85a7300640cd","tid":419642,"uid":39734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"開頭都好唔慣 <br />\n而家既習慣係：按時間搵 <br />\n或者去返果條友個對話搵<br />\n因為an 機同ios唔同，ios係一個apple store 曬全部野（相/片），backup 搬野方便啲"},{"pid":"b58fe4bea8127cad9b297a3c28b05068d35540fa","tid":419642,"uid":3549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:17:15.000Z","msg":"冇分類 上網/fb/wha